Name: assign_user_story_to_sprint_backlog
Description: 1 if user story is assigned to a sprint backlog; 0 otherwise (R11)

Name: assign_task_to_user_story
Description: 1 if task is assigned to a user story; 0 otherwise (R10)

Name: include_feature_in_release_plan
Description: 1 if feature is included in a release plan; 0 otherwise (R20)

Name: assign_team_to_project
Description: 1 if team is assigned to a project; 0 otherwise (R1)

Name: assign_scrum_master_to_team
Description: 1 if a Scrum Master supports a team; 0 otherwise (R6)

Name: assign_user_story_to_epic
Description: 1 if a user story belongs to an epic; 0 otherwise (R9)

Name: link_blocker_to_task
Description: 1 if blocker blocks a task; 0 otherwise (R16)

Name: attach_sprint_backlog_to_sprint
Description: 1 if sprint backlog belongs to a sprint; 0 otherwise (R12)

Name: invite_stakeholder_to_sprint_review
Description: 1 if stakeholder participates in a sprint review; 0 otherwise (R17)

Name: bind_velocity_to_team
Description: 1 if a velocity record refers to a team; 0 otherwise (R19)

Name: generate_snapshot_for_sprint
Description: 1 if a sprint generates a development snapshot; 0 otherwise (R22)

Name: assign_worker_to_team
Description: 1 if worker belongs to a team; 0 otherwise (R2)

Name: assign_skill_to_worker
Description: 1 if worker has a skill; 0 otherwise (R3)

Name: assign_role_to_worker
Description: 1 if worker takes on a role; 0 otherwise (R4)
